SSD drive

1. Enumeration: your client driver able to recognize your SSD
2. Block management:
     1TB ---> 900 GB already, 50 GB
     100 GB--> 50 GB
     format  --> 980 GB

3. 1000 GB, 100 GB user data,
900 GB free data---> 50 GB dta
--> flash fw, boot loader
